# HuggingFace Rules

- Call `prepare_model_for_kbit_training()` before attaching LoRA.
- Set tokenizer pad token for causal LM if missing.
- Use T4-safe precision defaults (`fp16=true`, `bf16=false`) on Kaggle T4.
- Prefer config-driven hyperparameters over inline constants.
- Save adapter checkpoints separately from base model weights.

